title: Jungler looking for ranked team
body:
Howdy, 
there really isnt much i can say about myself, i was previously a support (which i thought i was okay at) then a friend said for me to try rek'sai, now i can't stop playing her and my win rate is 77% of games which is pretty good im told. I can play warwick, evelynn, rammus, udyr and master yi in the jungle also and i am working on other junglers too. I havent played alot of ranked so far because im just practicing until i am able to carry close to 85% of games.
if you would like to hit me up for a chat my in game name is Blushift, i am looking for a team of any level, just one that is willing to improve and climb the ranks.
Thanks for taking the time to read this post.
